title: Ryosuke Kawano
text:
is a <a href="Japanese%20people">Japanese</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="Mito%20HollyHock">Mito HollyHock</a>.
Playing career.
Ryosuke Kawano played for <a href="J1%20League">J1 League</a> club; <a href="Shonan%20Bellmare">Shonan Bellmare</a> in 2013. In 2014 season, he move to <a href="J3%20League">J3 League</a> club; <a href="Fukushima%20United%20FC">Fukushima United FC</a>. In January 2018, after three seasons with <a href="Verspah%20Oita">Verspah Oita</a>, he signed for <a href="YSCC%20Yokohama">YSCC Yokohama</a>.

"Updated to 20 February 2020".
